        <updateDate>2020-04-20T15:22:16Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Protecting Rights Of Those Exploited by Coercive Trafficking Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill specifies that supplying, furnishing, or providing a drug or illegal substance to a person, including to exploit or create an addiction, constitutes (1) coercion, for purposes of a child sex trafficking offense; and (2) coercive means, for purposes of a forced labor offense.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
